snippet.title: Tum Kya Mile - Rocky Aur Rani Kii Prem Kahaani | Ranveer | Alia | Pritam | Amitabh | Arijit | Shreya
snippet.description:
This season, we invite you to fall in love with Tum Kya Mile from Rocky Aur Rani Kii Prem Kahaani.

Song Credits:
Singer: Arijit Singh & Shreya Ghoshal
Composer: Pritam
Lyrics: Amitabh Bhattacharya
Choreographer: Vaibhavi Merchant

Viacom18 Studios & Dharma Productions present
A Dharma Productions film
Rocky Aur Rani Kii Prem Kahaani
Starring Dharmendra, Jaya Bachchan, Shabana Azmi, Ranveer Singh & Alia Bhatt
Directed by Karan Johar
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar & Apoorva Mehta
Story & Screenplay by Ishita Moitra, Shashank Khaitan & Sumit Roy
Dialogues by Ishita Moitra

In cinemas on 28th July, 2023.
Pre-book your BMS voucher now: https://bookmy.show/RAR_Voucher

Music Arrangement and Production: Prasad Sashte
Additional Production: Rahul Tiwari and Himonshu Parikh
Piano Riff: Himonshu Parikh
Sound Design: DJ Phukan and Ashwin Kulkarni
Mix & Master: Shadab Rayeen at New Edge Chief Engineer: Ashwin Kulkarni
Shootmix: Pranav Gupta
Music Production Manager: Anurag Sharma

Chorus: Subhashree Das,Antara Bhattacharya, Rehaa, Shivangi Rammurty, Chaitalee Chhaya, Maanuni Desai, Shreya Phukan, Ana Rahman

Lyrics:
Berange thhe din
Berangi shaamein

Aayi hain tum se
Rangeeniyaan

Pheeke thhe lamhe
Jeene mein saare

Aayi hain tumse
Namkeeniyaan

Be-iraada raaston ki
Ban gaye ho manzilein

Mushkilein hul hain tumhi se
Ya tumhi ho mushkilein

Tum kya mile..
Tum kya mile..

Hum na rahe hum
Tum kya mile..

Jaise mere dil mein khile

Phaagun ke mausam
Tum kya mile..

Tum kya mile..
Tum kya mile..
Tum kya mile..
Tum kya mile..

Kore kaagazon ki hi tarha hai
Ishq bina jawaaniyaan

Darj hui hain shaayari mein
Jinki hain prem kahaaniyaan

Hum zamaane ki nigaahon
Mein kabhi gumnaam thhe

Apne charche kar rahi hain
Ab shaher ki mehfilein

Tum kya mile..
Tum kya mile..

Hum na rahe hum
Tum kya mile..

Jaise mere dil mein khile

Phaagun ke mausam
Tum kya mile..

Tum kya mile..
Tum kya mile..
Tum kya mile..
Tum kya mile..

snippet.title: নবাবের মন খারাপ কেন? | Gopal Bhar | Double Gopal | Full Episode
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SONY AATH Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBz9qbqujcjIavFmBJW2oZw?sub_confirmation=1

Click to watch all the episodes of Gopal Bhar -
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL5O3zv2ZcASiKOTRSEBzEwxlnw10AkNbE

Episode 890 - 891: নবাবের মন খারাপ কেন?
---------------------
The Nawab of Murshidabad is depressed, so he asks his montri to find a means to make him feel better. Gopal's wife creates a sweet treat called "Taler Bora" (sweet fritters). Will this sweet dish cheer up the Nawab?

About the show
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous, and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers

snippet.description:
Today in our village, We cook the Nalli biryani recipe using fresh lamb shanks. We use Seeraga samba rice to make this traditional biryani recipe. The special of this mutton recipe is while eating biryani, and we taste a lot of bone marrow with the meat.

We enjoy the biryani at the evening! The taste is delicious!

snippet.title: 'ആദ്യമായാണ് ഈ സമയത്ത് വീട്ടിൽ കിടന്നുറങ്ങുന്നത്'; ടെട്രാപോഡിൽ തീർന്നോ ചെല്ലാനത്തെ ദുരിതം ?
snippet.description:
Chellanam| ദുരിതക്കയത്തിലായിരുന്നു വർഷങ്ങളായി ചെല്ലാനം. മഴക്കാലത്ത് കടലാക്രമണം ഈ തീരദേശ പഞ്ചായത്തിനെ ദുരിതാശ്വാസ ക്യാമ്പുകളിലേക്ക് പറിച്ചുനട്ടിരുന്നു. എന്നാൽ, 304 കോടി ചെലവിൽ നിർമിച്ച ടെട്രാപോഡ് കടൽഭിത്തി ഇത്തവണ ഇവർക്ക് ആശ്വാസമായിരിക്കുകയാണ്. വലിയ മഴയോ കടലാക്രമണമോ ഉണ്ടായിട്ടില്ലെങ്കിലും ഭിത്തി നിർമിച്ച ഏഴു കിലോമീറ്റർ ദൂരത്തിൽ ഇതുവരെ പ്രശ്നങ്ങളൊന്നും ഉണ്ടായിട്ടില്ല. ടെട്രാപോഡ് ഭിത്തിയോടൊപ്പം നിർമിച്ച നടപ്പാത ടൂറിസത്തിനും വലിയ സാധ്യതകളാണ് ചെല്ലാനത്തിന് തുറന്നുകൊടുക്കുന്നത്. എന്നാൽ, ഇനിയും കടൽഭിത്തി നിർമിക്കാത്ത കണ്ണമാലി ഉൾപ്പെടെയുള്ള മേഖലകളിലെ ജനങ്ങൾ മുൻവർഷങ്ങളിലേതുപോലെ ആശങ്കയിലാണ് ഇപ്പോഴും.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3808 | 27 June 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3808: Jethalal Ke Priya Mitra
--------------------------------------------------------
The client finally meets with Jetha and Taarak, but Champaklal comes and unintentionally reveals the truth. The client is unhappy because Jethalal has been lying so far. Champaklal assures the clients that his son is innocent and that he never intended to conceal the truth. Jetha admits that he tried to avoid the encounter due to his poor command of the English language. The clients agreed to the terms after being impressed by Jetha's regard for his father. Taarak informs Jetha that he has come to assist Anjali at her request. Jetha later arranges an intimate dining experience for Taarak and his wife as an acknowledgment.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3808, 27 June 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 17 Teaser - 27th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 17 Teaser - 27th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Imran Abbas as Shani
Neelam Muneer as Shanzay
Nimra Khan as Sajeela
Mahmood Aslam as Kamran
Ismat Zaidi as Kulsoom
Maira Khan as Nadiya
Zainab Qayoom as Samiya
Saqib Sameer as Khawar
Aadi Khan as Jugnu
Birjees Farooqui as Farzana

Mirza Rizwan as Faiq

snippet.title: J & V United by Love |Jisma Vimal Wedding| #lovestory #weddingvideo #southindianwedding
snippet.description:
J & V United by Love |Jisma Vimal Wedding| #lovestory #weddingvideo #southindianwedding 

" " United by Love " is a documentary focused on our journey from starting out as friends and aspiring actors, to falling in love and making it big through YouTube and finally getting married to each other. We come from southern part of India and we feel lucky to have a successful relationship even though our families follow different religions. We personally thank "Enchanteur", a brand centered around romance & love, joining hands with us in celebrating our love and making it special . Riding towards more adventure in our life and career, we pause for a moment and share these precious moments with you all. 

Love always, 

J& V

Today we are making Ashadhi Ekadashi vishesh upwas thali. As everybody in the house fasts on this day and the fast lasts for 24 hours, just 1-2 upwas recipes are not enough. So I am showing you upwas thali. This thali contains upwas gulabjam, sabudana khichadi, varaicha bhat and amti, lal bhoplyachi bhaji, upwas vade and a ghavan. I am trying to make it healthier. You have to come up with some healthy and tasty fasting recipes. I am trying to help you. I already have shown 2-3 upwas thalis. You can make combinations according to your taste and choice. You can try this thali at home and drop a comment for me. Do not forget to like, share and subscribe.

Ingredients:
Sabudana Khichadi
• 1 cup Sabudana
• 1 cup Water
• 1 tsp Ghee
• 1 tsp Cumin seeds
• 2~3 chopped Green chilies
• 1 boiled and chopped Potato
• A little Salt
• 1/2 cup roasted Peanut powder
• Salt to taste  
Upwas Gulabjam
• 1 cup grated Khava / Khoya
• 1/4 cup grated Paneer
• 2 tsp Shingada flour
• A pinch of Baking soda
• 1 cup Sugar
• 1/2 cup Water
• 2 green Cardamom
• Oil for frying
Upwasache Vade
• 1/4 cup Sabudana
• 1 cup Varai
• 2 chopped Green chilies
• 1/4” grated Ginger
• 1 tsp Cumin seeds
• 1/2 cup grated Pumpkin
• 1/2 cup boiled and mashed Potato
• Salt to taste
• Chopped Green chili
• Oil for frying
Varaicha Bhat
• 1 tsp Ghee
• 1/2 cup Varai
• 1 1/2 cup hot Water
• Salt to taste
Upwasachi Amti
• 1 cup roasted Peanuts
• 2 chopped Green chilies
• Water as needed
• 1 tsp Ghee
• 1 tsp Cumin seeds
• Cinnamon
• 2 green Cardamom
• 4~5 Black peppercorns
• 1 Bay leaf
• Water to adjust consistency
• Salt to taste
• 2 tbsp Tamarind-Gudh pulp
Upwasachi Bhaji
• 1 tsp Ghee
• 1/2 tsp Cumin seeds
• 1/2 tsp Red chili powder
• 250 g chopped Pumpkin
• A little Water
• Salt to taste
• 2 tbsp grated fresh Coconut
Rajgira Ghavan
• 1/2 cup Rajgira flour
• Salt to taste
• Water as needed
• Oil / Ghee

For more Such Recipes

Today we are making Ashadhi Ekadashi vishesh upwas thali. As everybody in the house fasts on this day and the fast lasts for 24 hours, just 1-2 upwas recipes are not enough. So I am showing you upwas thali. This thali contains upwas gulabjam, sabudana khichadi, varaicha bhat and amti, lal bhoplyachi bhaji, upwas vade and a ghavan. I am trying to make it healthier. You have to come up with some healthy and tasty fasting recipes. I am trying to help you. I already have shown 2-3 upwas thalis. You can make combinations according to your taste and choice. You can try this thali at home and drop a comment for me. Do not forget to like, share and subscribe.

Ingredients:
Sabudana Khichadi
• 1 cup Sabudana
• 1 cup Water
• 1 tsp Ghee
• 1 tsp Cumin seeds
• 2~3 chopped Green chilies
• 1 boiled and chopped Potato
• A little Salt
• 1/2 cup roasted Peanut powder
• Salt to taste  
Upwas Gulabjam
• 1 cup grated Khava / Khoya
• 1/4 cup grated Paneer
• 2 tsp Shingada flour
• A pinch of Baking soda
• 1 cup Sugar
• 1/2 cup Water
• 2 green Cardamom
• Oil for frying
Upwasache Vade
• 1/4 cup Sabudana
• 1 cup Varai
• 2 chopped Green chilies
• 1/4” grated Ginger
• 1 tsp Cumin seeds
• 1/2 cup grated Pumpkin
• 1/2 cup boiled and mashed Potato
• Salt to taste
• Chopped Green chili
• Oil for frying
Varaicha Bhat
• 1 tsp Ghee
• 1/2 cup Varai
• 1 1/2 cup hot Water
• Salt to taste
Upwasachi Amti
• 1 cup roasted Peanuts
• 2 chopped Green chilies
• Water as needed
• 1 tsp Ghee
• 1 tsp Cumin seeds
• Cinnamon
• 2 green Cardamom
• 4~5 Black peppercorns
• 1 Bay leaf
• Water to adjust consistency
• Salt to taste
• 2 tbsp Tamarind-Gudh pulp
Upwasachi Bhaji
• 1 tsp Ghee
• 1/2 tsp Cumin seeds
• 1/2 tsp Red chili powder
• 250 g chopped Pumpkin
• A little Water
• Salt to taste
• 2 tbsp grated fresh Coconut
Rajgira Ghavan
• 1/2 cup Rajgira flour
• Salt to taste
• Water as needed
• Oil / Ghee

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 16 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 27th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Everyone is excited about renovation. Babita's brother is an architect, so he will be leading this project. Since Jethalal's dining table is broken, they sit down on the floor and have their dinner. There is a funny conversation which takes place between Gada family regarding the same. The next day, Saptarangi (Babita's brother) comes to Gokuldham society to take the measurements of all the houses. Stay tuned.  

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1780
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 
 
Click here  to Subscribe to the LIV Comedy channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch special videos of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah here:

snippet.title: इन्हे जुल्फे सवारने के अलावा कोई और तकलीफ दी.. तो तोड़ के तेरे पति के हाथ मे दूंगी | Madhuri Dixit
snippet.description:
Raju, a young man, is devoted to his stepmother as he only wishes to be showered with motherly love. However, his stepmother exploits his love to extort his wealth.

Movie - Beta (1992)
Star Cast - Anil Kapoor, Madhuri Dixit, Aruna Irani, Anupam Kher, Laxmikant Berde
Director – Indra Kumar
Producer – Indra Kumar, Ashok Thakeria
Cinematographer – Baba Azmi
Music Director – Anand-Milind
Lyricist – Dev Kohli, Naqsh Lyallpuri, Sameer
Story – K. Bhagyaraj
Screenplay - Gyandev Agniri , Rajiv Kaul, Praful Parekh
Dialogues - Kamlesh Pandey
Editor –  Hussain A. Burmawala

राजू, एक युवक, अपनी सौतेली माँ के प्रति समर्पित है क्योंकि वह केवल मातृ प्रेम से नहाना चाहता है। हालाँकि, उसकी सौतेली माँ उसकी दौलत निकालने के लिए उसके प्यार का फायदा उठाती है।

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 15 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream - 26th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Imran Abbas as Shani
Neelam Muneer as Shanzay
Nimra Khan as Sajeela
Mahmood Aslam as Kamran

Nehmat is taken aback upon discovering the serious complications in her pregnancy. Meanwhile, Sartaj recognizes her predicament and suggests that she should tell Ekam the whole truth about her pregnancy. Will Nehmat pay heed to his words?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

snippet.description:
Titanic submarine Missing: टलांटिक महासागर में 5 यात्रियों सहित गायब हुई टाइटन पनडुब्बी (Titanic submarine Missing) को लेकर कंपनी की तरफ से बताया गया है कि पनडुब्बी (Titanic submarine Missing) में सवार सभी 5 यात्रियों की मौत हो गई है. पनडुब्बी का मलबा टाइटेनिक जहाज (Titanic) के पास ही मिला है. दुनिया के सबसे बड़े और सबसे पॉपुलर जहाज रहे टाइटेनिक (Titanic Missing)को डूबे करीब 110 साल से भी ज्यादा का समय हो चुका है. इसका मलबा 1985 में ढूंढ लिया गया था.

राधाकृष्ण || RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part - 625 | Sankat Mein Radha  #radhakrishn #starbharat

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3807 | 26 June 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3807: Hum Meeting Ke Liye Taiyyar Hain
--------------------------------------------------------
Bagha and Nattu Kaka have been fully prepared for the meeting with the clients, while Jetha has decided to remain mute due to his English language difficulties. When the client arrives, Nattu Kaka and Bagha greet him, but they are more interested in speaking with the proprietor of Gada Shop. Clients inform them that they only hold business meetings with the firm owner and not with any of the employees. Taarak enters the scene at this point, and Bagha addresses him as their supervisor to handle the situation. Finally, the clients agree on the meeting's agenda. Will Gada Electronics secure the deal, or will the meeting be a flop?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3807, 26 June 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Bagha and Nattu Kaka have been fully prepared for the meeting with the clients, while Jetha has decided to remain mute due to his English language difficulties. When the client arrives, Nattu Kaka and Bagha greet him, but they are more interested in speaking with the proprietor of Gada Shop. Clients inform them that they only hold business meetings with the firm owner and not with any of the employees. Taarak enters the scene at this point, and Bagha addresses him as their supervisor to handle the situation. Finally, the clients agree on the meeting's agenda. Will Gada Electronics secure the deal, or will the meeting be a flop?

Nehmat is overjoyed after seeing her unborn child's sonography report. However, her happiness is shattered when she receives devastating news about her baby's concerning health condition. What will she do in this situation?

snippet.title: Jethalal से कैसे टूट गया Dining Table? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Comedy Express
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Jethalal, Taarak, Bhide, Sodhi and others try to lift Doctor Haathi from the broken sofa. Jetha’s hand got slipped, and eventually, he hits the dining table. The glass table got scattered. Everyone gets scared at that time. Watch the full clip for hilarious moments. Stay tuned. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1778
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 
 
Click here  to Subscribe to the LIV Comedy channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch special videos of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah here:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cQA3TWG8mHLCRO_vFhMoYiV

snippet.title: Living like a Mermaid 🧜‍♀️ for a day!
snippet.description:
🧜‍♀️ Living Like a Mermaid for a Day! 🌊 Dive into an enchanting underwater adventure as we take on the ultimate mermaid challenge. Join us on this magical journey as we transform into mermaids and explore the wonders of the ocean! 🐠

In this captivating vlog, we'll show you how we prepared for our day as mermaids, including getting our mermaid tails, creating mesmerizing mermaid makeup looks, and styling our hair with shimmering shells and pearls. 🧜‍♀️✨

Once we're fully transformed, we'll take you along as we dive into the crystal-clear waters, swimming gracefully like real mermaids. Get ready to witness stunning underwater footage as we encounter colorful marine life, mystical coral reefs, and maybe even discover hidden treasures! 🐚🌈

But being a mermaid isn't just about swimming. We'll also indulge in delightful mermaid-themed snacks and drinks, perfecting our mermaid poses and dances, and enjoying the magical serenity of the ocean's embrace. It's a day filled with joy, wonder, and a touch of mermaid magic! 🌊🎉

So, if you've ever wondered what it's like to live as a mermaid, or simply want to embark on a whimsical adventure with us, don't miss this extraordinary experience. Dive into the deep blue with us and let your imagination swim free in this unforgettable mermaid journey! 🧜‍♀️💙

Don't forget to like, comment, and subscribe to our channel to stay tuned for more incredible adventures. Hit that notification bell so you never miss a moment of our magical escapades! 🔔✨

Episode 5 - 6: ভেজাল দুধ
---------------------
Raja Krishnachandra has a new cow in his castle and instructs his attendants to offer him a glass of milk after dinner every night. Montri begins stealing the luscious creamy milk in order to avoid being detected. He begins to add water to it, thereby adulterating it. , how will Gopal catch the Montri this time? Keep an eye out!

About the show
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous, and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers

राधाकृष्ण || RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part - 623  |  Radha Ko Gai Gopiyon Ki Chinta #radhakrishn   #starbharat 

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!
